    {
      "id": 18,
      "gridPos": {
        "w": 24,
        "h": 5,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 86
      },
      "type": "text",
      "title": "System Overview",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "##  Helios Observability Platform\n\n**Event-Driven ML Anomaly Detection with AI-Powered PDF Reports**\n\n### Key Features:\n- **Real-time Ingestion**: Sub-30ms P99 latency\n- **ML Detection**: Isolation Forest anomaly detection\n- **AI Reports**: Claude 3.5 Sonnet generates professional PDF incident reports\n- **Storage**: TimescaleDB time-series database + Kafka streaming\n\n### Current Stats:\n- 14 microservices | 3K+ events/hour | 10 reports generated | $0.02-0.05 per report"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "gridPos": {
        "w": 24,
        "h": 10,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 76
      },
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Recent Anomalies \u2014 Top SHAP Feature",
      "description": "Last 20 anomalies with the single top SHAP-attributed feature driving the score. Negative SHAP pushes the IsolationForest score lower (more anomalous).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "grafana-postgresql-datasource",
        "uid": "helios-timescaledb"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "rawSql": "SELECT\n  time AS \"Time\",\n  service AS \"Service\",\n  severity AS \"Severity\",\n  ROUND(score::numeric, 3) AS \"IF score\",\n  (features->'top_features'->0->>'name') AS \"Top feature\",\n  ROUND(((features->'top_features'->0->>'value')::numeric), 3) AS \"Value\",\n  ROUND(((features->'top_features'->0->>'shap')::numeric), 3) AS \"SHAP\",\n  (features->'top_features'->0->>'direction') AS \"Direction\"\nFROM anomalies\nWHERE time > NOW() - INTERVAL '24 hours'\n  AND features ? 'top_features'\nORDER BY time DESC\nLIMIT 20",
          "format": "table",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "grafana-postgresql-datasource",
            "uid": "helios-timescaledb"
          }
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "align": "left"
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Severity"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "mappings",
                "value": [
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "CRITICAL": {
                        "color": "red",
                        "index": 0
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "HIGH": {
                        "color": "orange",
                        "index": 1
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "MEDIUM": {
                        "color": "yellow",
                        "index": 2
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "value",
                    "options": {
                      "LOW": {
                        "color": "blue",
                        "index": 3
                      }
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.displayMode",
                "value": "color-background"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "overwrite": true,
  "inputs": [],
